event ApproveTransaction(uint256 indexed id, address approver, string comment)
event CreateTransaction(uint256 indexed id, bytes[] data, uint256 deadline, uint8 status, string comment, address creator)
event ExecuteTransaction(uint256 indexed id, bytes[] data, address _executor)
event ExecuteUniswapInTransaction(uint256 indexed id, address indexed executor, address indexed toAddress, address token, uint256 amount)
event ExecuteUniswapOutTransaction(uint256 indexed id, address indexed executor, address indexed toAddress, address token, uint256 amount)
event ExecuteWETH9Transaction(uint256 indexed id, address indexed executor, address indexed toAddress, address tokenIn, address tokenOut, uint256 amount)
function assetBaseCurrencyPrice(address asset, uint256 amount) view returns (uint256)
function assetEthPrice(address asset, uint256 amount) view returns (uint256)
function createTransaction(bytes[] _data, uint32 _deadline, bool _isExecute, string comment) payable returns (uint256)

function decodeUniswapMulticall(bytes rawData, uint256 value, bytes response) view returns (tuple(address recipient, address tokenIn, address tokenOut, uint256 amountIn, uint256 amountOut, uint8 resultType)[] multicalData)
function decodeWETH9Call(bytes data, uint256 value) pure returns (address tokenIn, address tokenOut, uint256 amount)
function ethAssetPrice(address asset, uint256 ethAmount) view returns (uint256)

function exactInput(tuple(bytes path, address recipient, uint256 amountIn, uint256 amountOutMinimum) params) pure returns (tuple(address recipient, address tokenIn, address tokenOut, uint256 amountIn, uint256 amountOut, uint8 resultType))

function exactInputSingle(tuple(address tokenIn, address tokenOut, uint24 fee, address recipient, uint256 amountIn, uint256 amountOutMinimum, uint160 sqrtPriceLimitX96) params) pure returns (tuple(address recipient, address tokenIn, address tokenOut, uint256 amountIn, uint256 amountOut, uint8 resultType))

function exactOutput(tuple(bytes path, address recipient, uint256 amountOut, uint256 amountInMaximum) params) pure returns (tuple(address recipient, address tokenIn, address tokenOut, uint256 amountIn, uint256 amountOut, uint8 resultType))

function exactOutputSingle(tuple(address tokenIn, address tokenOut, uint24 fee, address recipient, uint256 amountOut, uint256 amountInMaximum, uint160 sqrtPriceLimitX96) params) pure returns (tuple(address recipient, address tokenIn, address tokenOut, uint256 amountIn, uint256 amountOut, uint8 resultType))

function initialize(tuple(address executor, uint256 executorTeamId, address[] approvers, uint256 approverTeamId, uint256 minApproval, string text, string transactionType, uint256 startTime, uint256 endTime, bool allowUnlimitedUsageCount, uint256 usageCount, address team) params, address[] _fromTokens, bool _allowAllToTokens, address[] _toTokens, bool _allowAnyAmount, uint256 _totalAmount, uint8 _amountPercentage, address _baseCurrency)
function refundETH() pure returns (tuple(address recipient, address tokenIn, address tokenOut, uint256 amountIn, uint256 amountOut, uint8 resultType))

function selfPermit(address, uint256, uint256, uint8, bytes32, bytes32) pure returns (tuple(address recipient, address tokenIn, address tokenOut, uint256 amountIn, uint256 amountOut, uint8 resultType))

function swapExactTokensForTokens(uint256 amountIn, uint256 amountOutMin, address[] path, address recipient) pure returns (tuple(address recipient, address tokenIn, address tokenOut, uint256 amountIn, uint256 amountOut, uint8 resultType))

function swapTokensForExactTokens(uint256 amountOut, uint256 amountInMax, address[] path, address recipient) pure returns (tuple(address recipient, address tokenIn, address tokenOut, uint256 amountIn, uint256 amountOut, uint8 resultType))

function sweepToken(address token, uint256 amountMinimum, address recipient) pure returns (tuple(address recipient, address tokenIn, address tokenOut, uint256 amountIn, uint256 amountOut, uint8 resultType))
function transactions(uint256) view returns (uint256 id, uint8 status, uint32 deadline, bool isExist, uint256 approvedCount)
function unwrapWETH9(uint256 amountMinimum, address recipient) pure returns (tuple(address recipient, address tokenIn, address tokenOut, uint256 amountIn, uint256 amountOut, uint8 resultType))
